dct_title_s: Austriae Ducatus seu Pannoniae Superioris chorographia
dct_description_sm: germana summa fide ac industria elaborata a Wolfgango Lazio.
2 bar scales on map, given in "Miliaria Germanica", "magna" and "parva".
Plate XI from Speculum orbis terrarum, part 2, Antwerpen, 1578.
From De Jode's Speculum orbis terrarum, Antwerp, first published in 1578.
